<inglise> Having regard to the Act of Accession of Austria, Finland and Sweden, and in particular Articles 11(2) and 16 of Protocol No 9 thereto, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Austria, Soome ja Rootsi &uuml;hinemisakti, eriti selle protokolli nr 9 artikli 11 l&otilde;iget 2 ja artiklit 16, </eesti>
